    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This specimen boasts a comprehensive service history with critical preventative maintenance completed, including a Vanos overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and rear subframe reinforcement. The powertrain remains unmodified, retaining its factory individual throttle bodies for razor-sharp throttle response. The chassis dynamics are preserved through original suspension geometry and a functional M-variable differential lock. The exterior finish exhibits excellent depth and clarity, reflecting a strictly climate-controlled life. This is a mechanically sorted, investment-grade icon for the purist.",
