      "description": "This E46 M3 is a definitive purist\u2019s specimen, powered by the S54 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise gates, feeding a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. This example is mechanically sorted with documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure long-term structural integrity. The chassis is dampened by a refreshed suspension setup, maintaining original geometry and tactile feedback. Inside, the Nappa leather shows no bolster wear, and the dash remains free of pixel degradation. Finished in its original factory paint with exceptional depth, this is an investment-grade enthusiast car.",
